Chris Evans, who plays the role of Captain America, has said that Marvel 4 might be his last cast in Marvel 4. He told New York Times that he’d like to leave before he is told. He told the publication “You want to get off the train before they push you off”. He has been in the film’s production since its first in 2011 starring as Captain America: The First Avenger, Avenger: Infinity War and Avengers 4. Avengers 4 will be released in May 2019.